Package model.productcontainer

Class Summary
ProductContainer The ProductContainer is the base class for ProductGroup and for StorageUnit.
ProductGroup The ProductGroup class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "ProductGroup".
ProductGroupVault The Product class provides a way to query for ProductModels within the select data backend (A Model superclass or interface could be created for this)
StorageUnit The StorageUnit class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "StorageUnit".
StorageUnitVault The Product class provides a way to query for ProductModels within the select data backend (A Model superclass or interface could be created for this)
